To see the cards that we modify or create on the host machine inside the container, need to bind it:
[mmehmood@minervagpvm01 interactive]$ singularity exec --bind /exp/minerva/app/users/mmehmood/MAT_AL9/GitRepo-Analysis/ana/
                                      NUISANCE_TUTORIAL/nuisance_tutorials/interactive:/interactive nuisance_nuint2024.sif /bin/bash
...broke the path there to fit on next line

Can fix this problem: Error in <TFile::TFile>: file /interactive/MC_inputs/MC_inputs/FRW_flux_LE.root does not exist
Flux histogram ROOT file '${PWD}/MC_inputs/FRW_flux_LE.root' does not exist!

by using the absolute path inside the container:
EVCT-FILENM  '/interactive/MC_inputs/FRW_flux_LE.root'
